        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">FYI, the pets are treated as a buff icon.  They stay when you log, zone, whatever till you click it off or unfortunately it is dispelled.  Seems that the base summon goes up every so often but never higher then light blue con to the caster.</P><P>On a positive note, with it being a buff icon, if your Warder runs off after something you just have to click the buff off.  Much better pet control.</P><P>Infernall Cryptwalker - lvl 51<BR><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=42507" target="_blank">http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=42507</a><BR>Goody Nature Server</P><P><i>"Time is meaningless to one who lives an eternity."</i><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
